  "texts": [
    "In addition, an elevator fault diagnosis system platform based on digital twin is established.",
    "The accuracy and practicality of the fault diagnosis system is confirmed by experimental validation.",
    "The elevator fault diagnosis based on digital twin model is realized.",
    "The main conclusions are as follows:",
    "(1) Digital twin technology combined with sensor data collection enables real-time visual monitoring of elevator operating conditions."
  ]
}